title: Hawkwind 2000-10-21 Brixton - HAWKESTRA -MP3
description:
Hawkestra, Brixton 2000 - the MP3s

Much has been said and written about this Hawkwind reunion show... it was quite a night!

Quality 6 or 7, it varies. Vocals are clear pretty much throughout, sometimes much of it is clear (eg violin and sax on Master.)
